<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
   <meta charset="utf-8">
   <title>Liebes-Orakel</title>
   <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Petit+Formal+Script">
   <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
   <style>
      * { box-sizing: border-box }

      body {
         padding-bottom: 50px;
         font: normal 18px/24px 'Petit Formal Script', fantasy;
      }

      h1 { margin-top: 10px; }
      h2 { margin: 0 0 20px; }

      .lovebox {
         width: 500px;
         margin: 20px auto;
         padding: 20px;
         border-radius: 20px;
         background-color: rgba(255,0,0,.5);
         box-shadow: 0 0 10px white;
         color: #FCBDEA;
         text-align: center;
         text-shadow: 1px 1px darkred;
      }

      .form { display: flex; }

         .form > * + * { margin-left: 20px; }

         .form input[type="text"] {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 100px;
            padding: 5px 20px 0;
            border: 0;
            border-radius: 20px;
            background-color: lightpink;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px lightpink;
            color: darkred;
            font: bold 14px/2 'Petit Formal Script', fantasy;
         }

         .form button {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border: 0;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: lightpink;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px lightpink;
            color: darkred;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1;
            animation: pulse 1s ease infinite alternate;
         }

         @keyframes pulse {
            to { transform: scale(1.3); }
         }

      .score {
         display: block;
         margin: 0;
         padding: 20px 0 0;
         text-shadow: 5px 5px 5px darkred;
         font-size: 124px;
         line-height: 1;
      }

      .statement {
         font-size: 24px;
         margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .archive-list {
         display: inline-block;
         margin: 0;
         padding: 0;
         list-style: none;
         text-align: left;
         line-height: 2;
         letter-spacing: 1px;
      }

      .archive-list strong { padding: 0 20px; }

      .footer {
         position: fixed;
         bottom: 0;
         left: 50%;
         margin-left: -250px;
         padding: 10px 20px 5px;
         font-size: 80%;
      }

         .footer > p {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
         }

      .hearty-bg {
         background:
            radial-gradient(circle closest-side at 60% 43%, #b03 26%, rgba(187,0,51,0) 27%),
            radial-gradient(circle closest-side at 40% 43%, #b03 26%, rgba(187,0,51,0) 27%),
            radial-gradient(circle closest-side at 40% 22%, #d35 45%, rgba(221,51,85,0) 46%),
            radial-gradient(circle closest-side at 60% 22%, #d35 45%, rgba(221,51,85,0) 46%),
            radial-gradient(circle closest-side at 50% 35%, #d35 30%, rgba(221,51,85,0) 31%),
            radial-gradient(circle closest-side at 60% 43%, #b03 26%, rgba(187,0,51,0) 27%) 50px 50px,
            radial-gradient(circle closest-side at 40% 43%, #b03 26%, rgba(187,0,51,0) 27%) 50px 50px,
            radial-gradient(circle closest-side at 40% 22%, #d35 45%, rgba(221,51,85,0) 46%) 50px 50px,
            radial-gradient(circle closest-side at 60% 22%, #d35 45%, rgba(221,51,85,0) 46%) 50px 50px,
            radial-gradient(circle closest-side at 50% 35%, #d35 30%, rgba(221,51,85,0) 31%) 50px 50px;

         background-color: #b03;
         background-size: 100px 100px;
      }
   </style>
</head>
<body class="hearty-bg">

   <header class="header lovebox">
      <h1>Finde die wahre Liebe</h1>
      <strong>Gib den Namen deines Schatzes ein und erfahre, ob ihr für einander bestimmt seid.</strong>
   </header>

   <form class="form lovebox" action="/" method="GET">
      <input type="text" name="name_du" placeholder="Dein Name" value="<%= name_du %>">
      <input type="text" name="name_schatzi" placeholder="Schatzis Name" value="<%= name_schatzi %>">
      <button type="submit">♥</button>
   </form>

   <% if (score) { %>
      <div class="result lovebox">
         <p class="statement">Ihr passt zu</p>
         <p class="score"><%= score %>%</p>
         <p class="statement">zusammen.</p>
         <p class="statement"><%= statement %></p>
      </div>
   <% } %>

   <footer class="footer lovebox">
      <p>Wir übernehmen keine Haftung für gebrochene Herzen.</p>
   </footer>

</body>
</html>
